  <name>Discord Drawing RPC</name>
  <summary>Share your drawing activity on Discord</summary>
  <icon type="stock">com.TheGameratorT.DiscordDrawingRPC</icon>
  <description>
    <p>
      A native desktop application that lets you share your drawing progress with Discord friends through Rich Presence.
    </p>
    <p>
      Discord Drawing RPC allows you to update your friends with a preview of your drawings directly in your Discord status. 
      Whether you're working on digital art, sketches, or any creative work, your friends can see what you're creating in real-time.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Lightweight native application</li>
      <li>System tray integration - runs quietly in the background</li>
      <li>Cross-platform support</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  <launchable type="desktop-id">com.TheGameratorT.DiscordDrawingRPC.desktop</launchable>
  <screenshots>
